 that\ncryptography is sometimes applied incorrectly in those that do. This implies\nthat a potentially large number of corresponding BLE peripheral devices are\nvulnerable to unauthorized data access.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Aug 2018 09:14:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Nov 2018 10:53:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 16 Feb 2019 00:55:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-19"}
