 human experts. ESSMArT can help Brightsquid\nto (i) minimize the impact of staff turnover and (ii) shorten the cycle from an\nissue being reported to an assignment to a developer to fix it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Aug 2018 13:04:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-14"}
